parameters: Pony-Celes: "If you don't want to get hurt, you better step aside!"
01_ポニーセレス_戦闘むすっと

Minion: "Are you sure about this? Going any further means you're
heading to meet Lord Octo-Darg."
Minion: "I can't believe the invincible Pony-Celes has a weakness."
Minion: "And it's octopuses, of all things. This is priceless!"

Minion: "There's no way a coward who runs away in desperation like you
can defeat Lord Octo-Darg."

Pony-Celes: "I-I'm not weak to octopuses or anything... I was just a
little surprised, but I'm fine now..."
Pony-Celes: "I'll take down Octo-Darg in no time..."

Minion: "Hah? No way that's going to happen. You won't stand a chance
against Lord Octo-Darg!"
Minion: "Besides, you're about to get beaten up by me right now."

Pony-Celes: "Look who's talking. A weak minion like you is feeling
pretty bold today!"

Pony-Celes: "As if you could do anything without borrowing Octo-
Darg's power."
Pony-Celes: "Well, what's it going to be? Come at me!"
Minion: "Yeah, I don't need to be told!"
01_ポニーセレス_戦闘むすっと
Pony-Celes: "Honestly, there's no way you could ever beat me."
Pony-Celes: "But... maybe what he said is true."
Pony-Celes: "Just seeing an octopus drains all my strength..."
